attributes.action: Increase aid and support for Palestinians
attributes.additional_details: Help Palestinians from the ongoing poor treatment they endure which includes displacement from homes, restricted access to basic resources, allegations of human rights. Palestinians have faced long-standing challenges, including displacement, limited access to clean water, healthcare, education. The UK Government must intervene to do all it can to alleviate their suffering.
attributes.background: Alleviate the crisis faced by people of Palestine. Increase aid and support to provide essential services, food, clean water, and medical assist to Palestinians. Advocate the protection of Palestinians, from violence and displacement. Provide immediate relief and long-term support to Palestinians.
